quran[15]{c,v,t}:
  54,41,And indeed the warnings came unto the House of Pharaoh
  54,42,"They denied Our signs—all of them; so We seized them with the seizing of One Mighty, Omnipotent"
  54,43,Are your disbelievers better than those? Or have you some exemption in the scriptures
  54,44,"Or do they say, “We are a host victorious!”"
  54,45,"The whole shall be routed and they will turn [their] backs"
  54,46,"Nay! The Hour is their tryst, and the Hour is more calamitous and more bitter"
  54,47,Truly the guilty are astray and mad
  54,48,"On the Day they are dragged upon their faces into the Fire, “Taste the touch of Saqar.”"
  54,49,Truly We have created everything according to a measure
  54,50,"And Our Command is naught but one, like the blinking of an eye"
  54,51,We have indeed destroyed the likes of you; so is there any who remembers
  54,52,Everything that they have done is in the scriptures
  54,53,everything small and great is inscribed
  54,54,Truly the reverent are amidst Gardens and a stream
  54,55,upon a seat of truth before an Omnipotent King